    "• Sina Weibo 9: a dataset collected based on the claims reported on www. weibo.",
    "where each claim contains text, image URL, response and so on.",
    "• FakeNewsNet 10: it contains two datasets collected using ground truths from Politifact and Gossipcop.",
    "The first collection was acquired from FakeNewsNet repository, which contains news of famous people, fact-checked by the GossipCop website.",
    "We provide examples from two popular datasets, LIAR and Twitter15, in Table 4 to help readers comprehend the content and labeling of the datasets more clearly."
